OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FWireless Festival has been cancelled
OL,7,Fafter Kanye West was blocked from
OL,8,Fentering the UK ahead of his scheduled
OL,9,Fheadline performance.
OL,11,F"The Home Office has withdrawn YE's
OL,12,FETA, denying him entry into the United
OL,13,FKingdom. As a result, Wireless
OL,14,FFestival is cancelled and refunds will
OL,15,Fbe issued to all ticket-holders,"
OL,16,FWireless said in a statement.
OL,18,F"As with every Wireless Festival,
OL,19,Fmultiple stakeholders were consulted
OL,20,Fin advance of booking YE and no
OL,21,Fconcerns were highlighted at the time."
OL,26,@sD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
