OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FWest, who also goes by the name Ye,
OL,7,Fmade an application to travel to the
OL,8,FUK on Monday, which was blocked by the
OL,9,Fgovernment, ITV News understands.
OL,11,FThe decision was made on the grounds
OL,12,Fthat his presence would not be
OL,13,Fconducive to the public good.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FThe Wireless statement continued:
OL,7,F"Antisemitism in all its forms is
OL,8,Fabhorrent, and we recognise the real
OL,9,Fand personal impact these issues have
OL,10,Fhad. As YE said today, he acknowledges
OL,11,Fthat words alone are not enough, and
OL,12,Fin spite of this still hopes to be
OL,13,Fgiven the opportunity to begin a
OL,14,Fconversation with the Jewish community
OL,15,Fin the UK."
OL,17,FThe announcement of West as a
OL,18,Fheadliner at Wireless drew criticism
OL,19,Ffrom Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,20,Fand multiple Jewish organisations over
OL,21,Fhis history of antisemitism.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
