PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FDowning Street had said "all options
OL,7,Fremain on the table" as West's
OL,8,Fapplication was being reviewed,
OL,9,Fstating that decisions are taken on a
OL,10,F"case-by-case basis, in line with the
OL,11,Flaw".
OL,13,FIn response to the building backlash,
OL,14,FWest said on Tuesday he wanted to meet
OL,15,Fwith the UK Jewish community in person
OL,16,Fwhen he came to London.
OL,26,@nD@YOUoD@TO]rD@AOUsD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,F"I've been following the conversation
OL,7,Faround Wireless and want to address it
OL,8,Fdirectly. My only goal is to come to
OL,9,FLondon and present a show of change,
OL,10,Fbringing unity, peace, and love
OL,11,Fthrough my music," the rapper said.
OL,13,F"I would be grateful for the
OL,14,Fopportunity to meet with members of
OL,15,Fthe Jewish community in the UK in
OL,16,Fperson, to listen.
OL,18,F"I know words aren't enough ` I'll
OL,19,Fhave to show change through my
OL,20,Factions. If you're open, I'm here."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
