PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FThe president of the Board of Deputies
OL,7,Fof British Jews said the group would
OL,8,Fbe willing to meet West "as part of
OL,9,Fhis journey of healing" but only after
OL,10,Fhe agreed not to play at Wireless.
OL,12,F"It has been less than a year since
OL,13,FKanye West released a song entitled
OL,14,FHeil Hitler, the culmination of three
OL,15,Fyears of appalling antisemitism," Phil
OL,16,FRosenberg said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,F"He also made a number of deeply
OL,7,Foffensive comments about the black
OL,8,Fcommunity, saying that the 400-year
OL,9,Fexperience of slavery was 'like a
OL,10,Fchoice'.
OL,12,F"Even while claiming remorse today,
OL,13,Fhis latest album includes a track
OL,14,Ffirst released last year with the
OL,15,Fabhorrent title Gas Chamber.
OL,17,F"The Jewish community will want to see
OL,18,Fa genuine remorse and change before
OL,19,Fbelieving that the appropriate place
OL,20,Fto test this sincerity is on the main
OL,21,Fstage at the Wireless Festival."
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
