PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FThe currently available version of
OL,7,FWest's latest album Bully, released
OL,8,Flast month, does not feature a song
OL,9,Fcalled Gas Chamber, but the song All
OL,10,FThe Love, which features CeeLo Green,
OL,11,Fwas reportedly titled Gas Chambers
OL,12,Fprior to its release.
OL,14,FPM Starmer called the decision for
OL,15,FWest to headline "deeply concerning"
OL,16,Flast week, as major sponsors withdrew
OL,17,Ftheir support for the festival over
OL,18,Fthe booking.
OL,26,@wD@ROUwD@dO]
