PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FPepsi and Diageo withdrew from the
OL,7,Ffestival, and no brands appeared as
OL,8,Fvisible sponsors on Wireless
OL,9,FFestival's official website on Monday
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,12,FAdditionally PayPal, which is a
OL,13,Fpayment partner for the annual rap and
OL,14,Fhip-hop festival, will not appear in
OL,15,Fany of its future promotional
OL,16,Fmaterials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
