PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FWest, who has not performed in the UK
OL,7,Fsince he headlined Glastonbury in
OL,8,F2015, has voiced admiration for Adolf
OL,9,FHitler and made numerous antisemitic
OL,10,Fremarks in the recent past.
OL,12,FLast year, he released a song called
OL,13,FHeil Hitler, a few months after
OL,14,Fadvertising a swastika T-shirt for
OL,15,Fsale on his website, and he has been
OL,16,Fbarred from X because of antisemitism
OL,17,Fon multiple occasions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
