SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FIt is understood that the Mayor of
OL,7,FLondon's office refused permission for
OL,8,Fthe London Stadium, in Stratford, to
OL,9,Fstage the rapper's concert this
OL,10,Fsummer, with sources citing community
OL,11,Fconcerns and the reputational impact
OL,12,Fon the city.
OL,14,FIn January, West took out a full-page
OL,15,Fadvert in the Wall Street Journal to
OL,16,Fapologise for his actions, titled: "To
OL,17,FThose I've Hurt".
OL,26,@xD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
