PN,31312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FWest said his bipolar disorder, linked
OL,7,Fto an undiagnosed brain injury, had
OL,8,Fled him to fall into "a four-month-
OL,9,Flong, manic episode of psychotic,
OL,10,Fparanoid and impulsive behaviour" that
OL,11,Fdestroyed his life.
OL,13,F"I am not a Nazi or an antisemite," it
OL,14,Fsaid. "I love Jewish people."
OL,26,@pD@VOUuD@AOUuD@cO]vD@GOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
