OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,FMelvin Benn, managing director at
OL,7,FFestival Republic, which promotes
OL,8,FWireless Festival, described himself
OL,9,Fas a "deeply committed anti-fascist"
OL,10,Fand "person of forgiveness" as he
OL,11,Fdefended the rapper's planned
OL,12,Fperformance.
OL,14,F"What Ye has said in the past about
OL,15,FJews and Hitler is as abhorrent to me
OL,16,Fas it is to the Jewish community, the
OL,17,FPrime Minister and others that have
OL,18,Fcommented and ` taking him at his word
OL,19,F` to Ye now also," Benn said.
OL,26,@qD@FOUqD@dO]rD@EOUrD@[O]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
