OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775646168
OL,3,CWireless Festival cancelled as Kanye
OL,4,CWest blocked from entering UK
OL,6,F"Ye's music is played on commercial
OL,7,Fradio stations in this country. It is
OL,8,Favailable via live streams and
OL,9,Fdownloads in this country without
OL,10,Fcomment or vitriol from anyone and he
OL,11,Fhas a legal right to come into the
OL,12,Fcountry and to perform in this country.
OL,14,F"He is intended to come in and
OL,15,Fperform. We are not giving him a
OL,16,Fplatform to extol opinion of whatever
OL,17,Fnature, only to perform the songs that
OL,18,Fare currently played on the radio
OL,19,Fstations in our country and the
OL,20,Fstreaming platforms in our country and
OL,21,Flistened to and enjoyed by millions."
